        use VVTerm for personal or commercial purposes, subject to these terms.
      </p>
      <p>
        These Terms apply to official VVTerm binaries distributed through Apple's App Store. Source code
        published at <a href={SITE.githubUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{SITE.githubUrl}</a>
        {" "}is licensed separately under GPL-3.0.
      </p>
      <h3>Free Version</h3>
      <p>
        The free version of VVTerm may be used without charge, subject to the following limitations:
        1 workspace, 3 servers, and 1 simultaneous connection.
      </p>
